high_descs: Head straight towards the sink by turning around and turning left.
Pick up butter knife from the sink.
Head towards the door, then hang a left and go to the counter top.
Place butter knife on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: Changing butter knife from one place to another.

high_descs: Turn right and turn left move towards the sink.
Pick the butter knife from the sink.
Turn right and turn left move towards the countertop.
Place the butter knife on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: To place the butter knife on the countertop.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight, turn left towards sink
Pick up butter knife from the sink
Turn around and go straight, turn left towards the counter top
Put the butter knife in the counter top
anns.task_desc: Placing the butter knife in the counter top
